# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  EXECO — Environment Variables
#  Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
#  Then fill in your values below
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. GEMINI AI (Default AI Provider — FREE)
#    Get your free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#    Model: gemini-2.5-flash (free tier, no billing needed)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. ADMIN PANEL PASSWORD
#    Set any string you want — this protects the admin panel.
#    Can also be changed in-app via the Admin Panel UI.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_ADMIN_PASSWORD=your_secret_admin_password

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. WALLETCONNECT PROJECT ID (Optional)
#    Required only if you want WalletConnect / mobile wallets.
#    MetaMask works perfectly WITHOUT this.
#    Get free at: https://cloud.walletconnect.com
#    A public fallback is used if not set.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=your_walletconnect_project_id

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ✅ NO ALCHEMY KEY NEEDED
#    EXECO uses public RPC endpoints — no Alchemy, Infura, or
#    QuickNode account required. Everything works out of the box.
#    (You can use Alchemy RPCs by editing src/config/networks.ts
#     if you want higher rate limits in production)
#
# ✅ NO UNISWAP API KEY NEEDED
#    Swaps call the Uniswap V3 SwapRouter02 contract directly
#    using viem — no Uniswap SDK, no API key, no extra package.
#
# ✅ NO BRIDGE API KEY NEEDED
#    Bridge uses LayerZero endpoints directly (coming in v2).
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OTHER AI PROVIDERS (Optional — users can paste keys in Settings UI)
# These are optional pre-fills. Users can always paste them in-app.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...          # https://platform.openai.com
# VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=sk-ant-...      # https://console.anthropic.com
# VITE_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=...           # https://platform.deepseek.com
# VITE_GROK_API_KEY=xai-...           # https://console.x.ai
# VITE_MISTRAL_API_KEY=...            # https://console.mistral.ai

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT
# Add these same variables in:
# Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# Variable names: same as above (VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY, etc.)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
